screen_desc: The screenshot displays a mobile app interface with various account-related options. The menu includes sections such as "Invoice Information," "Saved Places," "Terms and Policies," "Map Contribution," "Support Center," "Driver Feedback," and "About Us." There are also options to change the passcode and select the language, which is set to English. Contact information is provided with an email option and a phone number. At the bottom, there is a "Sign out" option, and the app version is noted as "Xanh SM - v3.14.1(158)." The layout is clean and user-friendly, with icons accompanying some menu items.
